21:23.880 --> 21:24.630
<b>It's fine.</b>

21:25.630 --> 21:28.220
<b>Just keep coming back alive, Tatsumi.</b>

21:28.220 --> 21:31.680
<b>Right. I hope we can build a strong relationship together, Akame.</b>

21:32.720 --> 21:36.560
<b>What kind of relationship were you planning to build with your clothes off?</b>

21:36.560 --> 21:38.980
<b>You guys are the ones who stripped me!</b>

21:38.980 --> 21:39.730
<b>Okay.</b>

21:39.730 --> 21:42.730
<b>Next, you'll be trained by Mine. Good luck.</b>

21:42.730 --> 21:43.320
<b>Eh?</b>

21:43.690 --> 21:46.070
<b>Out of the frying pan and into the fire, huh?</b>

21:47.530 --> 21:49.570
